Friday, with $40 flex for use in the Retail operations. Flex will not carry forward from Summer 1 to Summer 2. \u2020 Price per meal based on 4 meals a day for 5 weeks (1 session) ÷ price. Figures do not account for FLEX Dollars or tax.                 FLEX RELOAD - 25% Discount on FLEX Summer meal plans listed above now include the FLEX Reload option.     PLAN FLEX PRICE TAX TOTAL   Reload 10 $10 $7.50 $0.62 $8.12   Reload 20 $20 $15.00 $1.24 $16.24   Reload 30 $30 $22.50 $1.86 $24.36   Reload 40 $40 $30.00 $2.48 $32.48   Reload 50 $50 $37.50 $3.09 $40.59   Reload 60 $60 $45.00 $3.71 $48.71   Reload 70 $70 $52.50 $4.33 $56.83   Reload 80 $80 $60.00 $4.95 $64.95   Reload 90 $90 $67.50 $5.57 $73.07   Reload 100 $100 $75.00 $6.19 $81.19    FLEX Reload option is for the Summer FLEX Plan and 5-Day Plan listed above only. FLEX Reload dollars will carry over from Summer 1 to Summer 2 sessions. To load FLEX dollars, you must visit the Dining Services office. NOTE: All unused FLEX Reload expires at the end of Summer 2 session, so be mindful of how much you add at a time.                Summer Commuter Plan 2017 These plans roll over semester to semester         # of Meals Price/Meal FLEX Base Tax Total Door Rate Savings   Commuter 160 160 $5.94 -0- $950 $78.38 $1028.38 $7.50 21%   Commuter 120 120 $6.25 -0- $750 $61.88 $811.88 $7.50 17%   Commuter 80 80 $7.00 -0- $560 $46.20 $606.20 $7.50 7%    These plans provide Cafeteria access Monday-Sunday. Does not include FLEX.                  SUMMER SESSION DATES Session I: Mon., June 5 \u2013 Sat., July 8  /  Session II: Sun., July 9 \u2013 Fri., Aug. 11 DINING HOURS: Monday-Friday Breakfast: 7:00am - 10:00amLunch: 11:00am - 2:00pmDinner: 4:30pm - 7:00pm Saturday-Sunday Breakfast: 7:00am - 10:00amLunch: 11:00am - 1:30pmDinner: 4:30pm - 6:30pm For Bruce Cafeteria, visit dining.unt.edu/brucehall For Retail Food Shops, visit dining.unt.edu/retail-shop-hours                           Follow Us  Tweets by @UNTdining          Like Us   